ygData.messageBody:
Well, lions are certainly not what I would suggest at lvl 6.. especially
without a big party. If I were you I'd concentrate on partying with at
least one of tank and taking on things together. It's nearly impossible to
solo well until lvl 12. Wizard spell are just too underpowered until that
level.

Tandayen, Dark Elf Wizard
